{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_01",
  "title": "ドタバタ！？トラブルクリスマス！ 1話 突然のトラブル！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様。クリスマスイベントに向けて",
      "startTime": 2.8666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "練習も捗っているみたいだな",
      "startTime": 6.4872381756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい。この五人でクリスマスライブをするって",
      "startTime": 9.1156463306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rui001.wav",
      "text": "言われた時は驚きましたけど……",
      "startTime": 12.3489797275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急にすまなかったな。この時期はみんな多忙で",
      "startTime": 14.8823129972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh002.wav",
      "text": "グループでスケジュールを合わせるのが難しくてね",
      "startTime": 18.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それで、イベント当日に都合が合うメンバーを集めたら",
      "startTime": 21.7305897713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rio001.wav",
      "text": "こんな新鮮な顔ぶれになったのね",
      "startTime": 26.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "イベントではクリスマスツリーの点灯式をして",
      "startTime": 29.0840364139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-smr001.wav",
      "text": "その後にミニライブをするんですよね",
      "startTime": 32.4840364774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "当日着る衣装のデザインも見ましたよ～",
      "startTime": 35.4173684757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-kkr001.wav",
      "text": "こころにぴったりの可愛い衣装でした",
      "startTime": 38.2507031441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「アイドルがサンタになってファンに笑顔を届ける」",
      "startTime": 41.4840366682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rei001.wav",
      "text": "……素敵なコンセプトの衣装ですよね",
      "startTime": 46.0173698108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "衣装のことも含めて、イベントに向けて",
      "startTime": 48.7840366682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh003.wav",
      "text": "提案ややりたいことがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 51.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "出来るだけ、みんなの希望に添えられるように",
      "startTime": 54.7330162049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh004.wav",
      "text": "調整するから……うん？　なんだ？",
      "startTime": 57.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_warp-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
